# Environment Variables for Z-Beam Contact Form

# Resend Email Service
# Get your API key from: https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

# Note: In production, add this to your Vercel environment variables:
# 1. Go to your Vercel project dashboard
# 2. Navigate to Settings > Environment Variables
# 3. Add RESEND_API_KEY with your actual API key
# 4. Make sure to add it for Production, Preview, and Development environments
